"""
Closed-Loop Supply Chain — Decision Support System (Digital Twin Layer)
=======================================================================
Structure:
  Forward : Suppliers --> Factories --> Warehouses --> Markets
  Return  : Markets   --> Factories  (recovered products)

This file adds on top of the simulation:
  1. LP Optimizer  : recommends production, remanufacturing and shipping
                     decisions each period by minimizing a weighted
                     combination of unmet demand + cost + CO2 emissions
  2. Scenario Testing : runs the simulation under different disruption
                        conditions and compares results

Weights for the three objectives are adjustable at runtime.
All cost and emissions parameters are placeholders — replace with
real company data when available.
"""

